{"tid":101888,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"林燕玲教你投資利是錢","createTime":"2017-01-31T08:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T02:20:13.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf812f6c5eae37b6fee4226a048ab485baba920","tid":101888,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"農曆新年最興奮當然是「逗利是」，不想飲飲食食花光了， 前美女主主播現為渣打認股證銷售副董事林燕玲，教下大家怎樣樣投資利是錢。 她表示如果利是錢不多的話，可以考慮買窩輪以小搏大，入場費往往低至幾百元至幾千元。至於選擇股份方面，可以選擇一些強勢股份例如騰訊或者是銀河娛樂，這兩隻股份在去年升了一倍，今年至今的表現都是跑贏大市。有興趣的朋友，不妨投資少許利是錢。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.sudden.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/SuddenWeekly/1042/640pixfolder/A1042_019_13026982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.sudden.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FSuddenWeekly%2F1042%2F640pixfolder%2FA1042_019_13026982.jpg&h=68415908&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98428f37ff3749dee9c38da7d5497dcf5bdb5420","tid":101888,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"又可以翻幾翻了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e171d7c24c305136d93ab994a2e5097688ee8e4","tid":101888,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54379e8b96a2490904df65da2800baef18ff40f","tid":101888,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"美女<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b294452a1bbf895681607dd8f796ac17bca3cc","tid":101888,"uid":46254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74d76d09d5f81ea95fba6e622ac2997baca354d","tid"